signatureAbility.signatureDescription: After securing a RAC catch, ballcarriers with this ability can quickly shift momentum, change direction, and turn the corner without sacrificing speed.
Receivers with this ability have a high success rate when creating separation on the last cut of any route.
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes 10-20 yards from the LoS.
Blockers with this ability will frequently attempt and win pull blocks
Blockers with this ability start every new blocking encounter with built-in resistance
Blockers with this ability gain blocker resistance points as a faster rate
Truly devastating receiving threats are the ones that catch and can't be caught. When they enter the zone, they have increased fakeout rates on spin/juke/hurdle after the catch.
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes less than 10 yards from the LoS, outside the numbers
Avoid stumbling when carrying the ball

The most tenacious defenders beat their blocks by sheer force of will. When they enter the zone, their rush move attempts are free.

Defenders with this ability do not need to spend a point on shed attempts during a run play
Defenders with this ability can reach out of engaged blocks to tackle or sack nearby ballcarriers.

signatureAbility.signatureActivationDescription: Make consecutive passes for 5+ yards in air
signatureAbility.signatureDescription: The best quarterbacks learn to take calculated risks. When they enter the zone, they can't be intercepted (by AI defenders) and have increased throw speed.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws inside the numbers (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws outside the numbers (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability receive better pass blocking from their offensive linemen.
When playing from behind, players with this ability can easily enter the Zone.
Passers with this ability have access to four extra hot routes during pre-play adjustments; make hot routes faster; and receive more immediate playmaker reactions from WRs.
